Pursuing&#3; the&#3; four&#3; policy&#3; goals&#3; can&#3; help&#3; governments&#3; create&#3; effective&#3; service&#3; delivery&#3;
mechanisms.&#3;
The&#3; four&#3; policy&#3; goals&#3; allow&#3; the&#3; government&#3; to&#3; increase&#3; innovation&#3; and&#3; strengthen&#3; accountability&#3; between&#3; the&#3;
