The&#3;first&#3;three&#3;of&#3;these&#3;policy&#3;goalsâ€“(1)&#3;encouraging&#3;innovation&#3;by&#3;providers,&#3;(2)&#3;holding&#3;schools&#3;accountable,&#3;and&#3;
