                                                                                                                                  16&#3;
&#3;
&#12;available&#3; school&#3; resources&#3; and&#3; student&#3; needs.&#3; NonÍ²state&#3; schools&#3; receiving&#3; public&#3; funding&#3; often&#3; operate&#3; under&#3;
