Policy&#3;goal&#3;4:&#3;Promoting&#3;diversity&#3;of&#3;supply&#3;&#3;

    By&#3; facilitating&#3; market&#3; entry&#3; for&#3; a&#3; more&#3; diverse&#3; set&#3; of&#3; providers,&#3; governments&#3; can&#3; increase&#3; the&#3; responsibility&#3;
    for&#3;results,&#3;as&#3;providers&#3;subsequently&#3;become&#3;directly&#3;accountable&#3;to&#3;citizens&#3;as&#3;well&#3;as&#3;to&#3;the&#3;state.&#3;&#3;
