academic&#3; outcomes&#3; of&#3; students&#3; in&#3; public&#3; schools.&#3; The&#3; authors&#3; find&#3; that&#3; a&#3; 1&#3; standard&#3; deviation&#3; increase&#3; in&#3; private&#3;
