required&#3; to&#3; meet&#3; government&#3; requirements&#3; and&#3; are&#3; not&#3; allowed&#3; to&#3; charge&#3; tuition&#3; fees.&#3; As&#3; a&#3; result,&#3; 95&#3; percent&#3; of&#3;
private&#3; school&#3; costsâ€”including&#3; costs&#3; of&#3; teachers&#3; and&#3; operationsâ€”are&#3; paid&#3; by&#3; the&#3; government.&#3; This&#3; engagement&#3;
began&#3;as&#3;part&#3;of&#3;the&#3;wider&#3;education&#3;reform&#3;under&#3;which&#3;the&#3;government&#3;conducted&#3;shortÍ²term&#3;training&#3;of&#3;all&#3;high&#3;
