                             x Government&#3;places&#3;no&#3;limits&#3;on&#3;the&#3;number,&#3;student&#3;enrollment,&#3;or&#3;location&#3;of&#3;
                               privately&#3; managed&#3; schools;&#3; government&#3; does&#3; not&#3; restrict&#3; tuition&#3; levels&#3; at&#3;
                               private&#3;independent&#3;schools.&#3;
