&#12;Chile&#3; meets&#3; the&#3; minimum&#3; standard&#3; (Established)&#3; on&#3; two&#3; of&#3; the&#3; policy&#3; goals&#3; (encouraging&#3; innovation&#3; by&#3; providers&#3;
and&#3; promoting&#3; diversity&#3; of&#3; supply).&#3; In&#3; terms&#3; of&#3; holding&#3; schools&#3; accountable&#3; for&#3; results,&#3; Chileâ€™s&#3; policies&#3; represent&#3;
